Source: tomato-host
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Andreas Teuchert <ant+devel@unix-ag.uni-kl.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.8.3

Package: tomato-host
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pve-qemu-kvm, vzctl, bridge-utils, iproute,
 grep, lsof, vzdump, tinc, ipfw3-2.6.32-4-pve, timeout, curl, tomato-hostserver, ucspi-tcp,
 rdiff, socat, gzip, tcpdump, vncterm, awk, tar
Description: Meta package to install packages needed for tomato
 * Tinc: tinc
 * KVM: pve-qemu-kvm, ucspi-tcp, socat
 * OpenVZ: vzctl, vzdump, vncterm
 * Custom packages: tomato-hostserver, ipfw3-2.6.32-4-pve
 * Not part of Proxmox VE: timeout, curl, rdiff, tcpdump
 * Part of Proxmox VE: bridge-utils, iproute, grep, lsof, gzip, awk, tar
